Class ItemStackHandlerWrapper

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.github.noeppi_noeppi.libx.inventory.ItemStackHandlerWrapper
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    net.minecraftforge.items.IItemHandler, net.minecraftforge.items.IItemHandlerModifiable

    public class ItemStackHandlerWrapper
extends java.lang.Object
implements net.minecraftforge.items.IItemHandlerModifiable
    Copied from Cucumber and modified. A wrapper for an IItemHandlerModifiable to be used as capability with extra slot limitations. Meant to be used as capability.
